    <published>2022-06-12T12:07:20.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-06-12T12:31:36.823Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="1-反向代理指向动态域名"><a href="#1-反向代理指向动态域名" class="headerlink" title="1. 反向代理指向动态域名"></a>1. 反向代理指向动态域名</h3><p>反向代理指向一个动态域名，域名指向的IP每隔一个周期就会变更，反向代理即会失效。</p><p>需要在nginx.conf中http段增加以下配置：</p><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs nginx"><span class="hljs-attribute">resolver</span> <span class="hljs-number">127.0.0.11</span> valid=<span class="hljs-number">300s</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其中127.0.0.11是nginx服务器的DNS服务地址，可以通过以下命令查看：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> /etc/resolv.conf<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>例子中的 <strong>127.0.0.11</strong> 为docker镜像中常见DNS。</p><h3 id="2-静态文件加速"><a href="#2-静态文件加速" class="headerlink" title="2. 静态文件加速"></a>2. 静态文件加速</h3><p>新建网站首页打开时非常慢，抓包看到有个JS文件体积1.5Mb，下载需要12.x秒。网管建议打开nginx gzip配置。</p><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs nginx"><span class="hljs-attribute">gzip</span>  <span class="hljs-literal">on</span>;<br><span class="hljs-attribute">gzip_min_length</span> <span class="hljs-number">1k</span>;<br><span class="hljs-attribute">gzip_comp_level</span> <span class="hljs-number">4</span>;<br><span class="hljs-attribute">gzip_types</span> text/plain application/javascript application/x-javascript text/javascript text/xml text/css;<br><span class="hljs-attribute">gzip_disable</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;MSIE [1-6]\.&quot;</span>;<br><span class="hljs-attribute">gzip_vary</span> <span class="hljs-literal">on</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>参考文档：</p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/wang_jing_jing/article/details/124250224">Nginx 性能优化 Gzip 压缩配置</a></p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/m0_68850571/article/details/124027158">Nginx配置性能优化（最详细总结）</a></p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
