    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>两个仓库执行git push操作，一个成功，一个失败</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git push --all origin                        <br>Enumerating objects: 2768, <span class="hljs-keyword">done</span>.<br>Counting objects: 100% (2768/2768), <span class="hljs-keyword">done</span>.<br>Delta compression using up to 8 threads<br>Compressing objects: 100% (957/957), <span class="hljs-keyword">done</span>.<br>Writing objects: 100% (2768/2768), 71.92 MiB | 197.97 MiB/s, <span class="hljs-keyword">done</span>.<br>Total 2768 (delta 1773), reused 2454 (delta 1604), pack-reused 0<br>error: RPC failed; HTTP 413 curl 22 The requested URL returned error: 413<br>send-pack: unexpected disconnect <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> reading sideband packet<br>fatal: the remote end hung up unexpectedly<br>Everything up-to-date<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>网上查了下，大概率是Nginx层有上传最大限制，查看nginx日志，果然有错误信息</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">2022/01/01 08:57:26 [error] 6<span class="hljs-comment">#6: *12 client intended to send too large body: 65444907 bytes, client: 100.100.100.100, server: git.example.com, request: &quot;POST /example/test_script.git/git-receive-pack HTTP/1.1&quot;, host: &quot;git.example.com&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>按网上提供的方案，本地放开限制</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git config http.postBuffer 524288000<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>同时nginx http段增加配置后重启</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ini">client_max_body_size 512m<span class="hljs-comment">;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>问题解决。</p><blockquote><p>参考文档：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/AV_woaijava/article/details/123101904">https://blog.csdn.net/AV_woaijava/article/details/123101904</a></p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
