  <entry>
    <title>包含SLB的环境缩容时提示some of the specified backend servers do not exist or are not running.</title>
    <link href="http://brianchenl.github.io/2022/05/26/slb_shrink_error/"/>
    <id>http://brianchenl.github.io/2022/05/26/slb_shrink_error/</id>
    <published>2022-05-26T12:21:50.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-06-02T14:04:41.060Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="问题现场"><a href="#问题现场" class="headerlink" title="问题现场"></a>问题现场</h3><p>使用<a href="https://www.cloudiac.org/" title="CloudIaC官网">CloudIaC</a>供给了一套高可用环境，SLB关联多个ECS instance。用户量下降后，根据需求减少ECS instance实例数量，执行环境更新操作时，给报错了。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">ansible_host.cloudiac_website[1]: Destroying... [<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span>=10.9.0.110]<br>ansible_host.cloudiac_website[1]: Destruction complete after 0s<br>alicloud_instance.instance[1]: Destroying... [<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span>=i-j6cfxch3hp19qbdi10dc]<br>alicloud_instance.instance[1]: Still destroying... [<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span>=i-j6cfxch3hp19qbdi10dc, 10s elapsed]<br>alicloud_instance.instance[1]: Destruction complete after 12s<br>alicloud_slb_server_group.default: Modifying... [<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span>=rsp-j6ctarh6aaavt]<br><br>Error: [ERROR] terraform-provider-alicloud/alicloud/resource_alicloud_slb_server_group.go:209: Resource rsp-j6ctarh6aaavt RemoveVServerGroupBackendServers Failed!!! [SDK alibaba-cloud-sdk-go ERROR]:<br>SDK.ServerError<br>ErrorCode: ObtainIpFail<br>Recommend: https://next.api.aliyun.com/troubleshoot?q=ObtainIpFail&amp;product=Slb<br>RequestId: 97B9EA25-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-0ABE26C845B4<br>Message: The specified BackendServers is invalid; some of the specified backend servers <span class="hljs-keyword">do</span> not exist or are not running.<br><br>  on main.tf line 70, <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> resource <span class="hljs-string">&quot;alicloud_slb_server_group&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;default&quot;</span>:<br>  70: resource <span class="hljs-string">&quot;alicloud_slb_server_group&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;default&quot;</span> &#123;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>第二次执行就成功。</p><h3 id="问题分析"><a href="#问题分析" class="headerlink" title="问题分析"></a>问题分析</h3><p>从日志中可以看到，先做了instance [id&#x3D;10.9.0.110] 的释放，再去更新slb_server_group资源时报了错。从控制台操作逻辑来说，应该是先将需要释放的instance从slb服务器组中删除，再进行销毁。应该是这个处理逻辑错乱出的错。给阿里云提工单！！</p><h3 id="解决结果"><a href="#解决结果" class="headerlink" title="解决结果"></a>解决结果</h3><p>2个月后的今天，阿里云终于给出了已修复的答复，试了下还是老问题，询问后得知需要增加一个资源配置，修改代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">resource <span class="hljs-string">&quot;alicloud_slb_server_group&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;default&quot;</span> &#123;<br>  load_balancer_id = alicloud_slb_load_balancer.default.id<br>  name             = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;cloudiac_server_group&quot;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment"># 注释掉原代码</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment"># servers &#123;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">#   server_ids = alicloud_instance.cloudiac.*.id</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">#   port       = &quot;80&quot;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">#   weight     = 50</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment"># &#125;</span><br>&#125;<br><br>resource <span class="hljs-string">&quot;alicloud_slb_server_group_server_attachment&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;ssga&quot;</span> &#123;<br>  count = var.instance_number<br>  server_group_id = alicloud_slb_server_group.default.id<br>  server_id = alicloud_instance.cloudiac[count.index].<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span><br>  port = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;80&quot;</span><br>  weight = 50<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>缩容执行结果：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">ansible_host.cloudiac_website[1]: Destroying... [<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span>=10.9.0.111]<br>ansible_host.cloudiac_website[1]: Destruction complete after 0s<br>alicloud_slb_server_group_server_attachment.ssga[1]: Destroying... [<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span>=rsp-j6ctarh6aaavt:i-j6c5hdcgb6fim7vq3vxe:80]<br>alicloud_slb_listener.default: Modifying... [<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span>=lb-j6cmx0wqg117iobg0pq00:https:443]<br>alicloud_slb_server_group_server_attachment.ssga[1]: Destruction complete after 0s<br>alicloud_instance.instance[1]: Destroying... [<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span>=i-j6c5hdcgb6fim7vq3vxe]<br>alicloud_slb_listener.default: Modifications complete after 1s [<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span>=lb-j6cmx0wqg117iobg0pq00:https:443]<br>alicloud_slb_listener.http: Modifying... [<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span>=lb-j6cmx0wqg117iobg0pq00:http:80]<br>alicloud_slb_listener.http: Modifications complete after 1s [<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span>=lb-j6cmx0wqg117iobg0pq00:http:80]<br>alicloud_instance.instance[1]: Still destroying... [<span class="hljs-built_in">id</span>=i-j6c5hdcgb6fim7vq3vxe, 10s elapsed]<br>alicloud_instance.instance[1]: Destruction complete after 12s<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以看到，在instance销毁之前，先做了 alicloud_slb_server_group_server_attachment 资源的变更，至此问题修复。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
